<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Krypton Bot | Dashboard</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-violet-500 mb-4">Krypton Bot</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-md">Gerencie os tickets de suporte do seu servidor Discord de maneira moderna e fácil através de nossa plataforma.</p>
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition">Ir para Painel</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/auth/login" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition">Entrar com Discord</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
